{"tid":826381,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"返工究竟幾時停","createTime":"2018-09-18T08:07:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T15:25:53.000Z","uid":140357,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"705e3d22750362430ed6b8e298f4b08a7460cb61","tid":826381,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:07:38.000Z","msg":"返工<br />\n返工2之放工<br />\n返工3之再次返工<br />\n返工4之愛放工<br />\n<br />\n交通不便,市民上下班有困難。而當大家去做義工清理自己社區,關注清潔工的辛勞。林鄭就自讃政府工作出色,自己領導同決策有方,社區安然渡過。别人的努力成為決策者的功績,所以如果你係香港人的話,除左做鍵盤戰士同義工,為左香港,請記住,20180917,香港只有香港人自救,政府的決策者係無幫過大家。"},{"pid":"0bf8fad05b81eca5462fedec8734201d197af2c9","tid":826381,"uid":198400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:55:20.000Z","msg":"直到死個日"},{"pid":"5903ed53f591239849b9b70fba1e346d27bdb588","tid":826381,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bf8fad05b81eca5462fedec8734201d197af2c9","tid":826381,"uid":198400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:55:20.000Z","msg":"直到死個日"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:57:21.000Z","msg":"退休個日姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed22b952d94e88ac306ec7ed5510f49f15d0c5e4","tid":826381,"uid":86383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T12:52:26.000Z","msg":"邊個發明返工，我請佢食米田共"},{"pid":"e2f907c69d14aaab9ba1d6963b0dd987be03e2ac","tid":826381,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T12:53:16.000Z","msg":"努力儲錢投資退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b38612880022ddb184a931cba13bac8a87b9ba","tid":826381,"uid":171594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5903ed53f591239849b9b70fba1e346d27bdb588","tid":826381,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bf8fad05b81eca5462fedec8734201d197af2c9","tid":826381,"uid":198400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:55:20.000Z","msg":"直到死個日"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime